<h2 id="bonus-part-2-markdown">Bonus (Part 2): Markdown</h2>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-markdown" data-lang="markdown"><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
2
3
4
